com.paypal.merchant.sdk.domain.shopping
Interface CartItem

public interface CartItem

An item you might be selling (an apple, a car, a one hour music lesson, etc.) It contains information such as the item name, an inventoryId that you define, a price, and a tax rate. These items can be placed into the ShoppingCart for use during a purchase via the TransactionManager.
